    <title>
        postcss: Make the resource cache key more stable
    </title>
    <updated>2022-05-27T16:38:44Z</updated>
    <media:thumbnail height="30" width="30" url="https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/394382?s=30&amp;u=0c57f8445a153dbc0991ae3adaecab4f542ce17f&amp;v=4"/>
    <author>
      <name>bep</name>
      <uri>https://github.com/bep</uri>
    </author>
    <content type="html">
      &lt;pre style=&#39;white-space:pre-wrap;width:81ex&#39;&gt;postcss: Make the resource cache key more stable

By using the input map as the basis, which means the hash will not change if we add/rename/remove options.

